{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/videos/recipes/vegan-kimchi-fried-rice","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Fried rice is a classic dish around the world.  It's usually a mix of leftover food and in different parts of the world, those can be different things. I love the idea of using kimchi because not only does in provide crunch and a ton of flavor, but the red from the chilis in its juice colors the rice beautifully.  It's a great vegan dish because you're not short of flavor and any additions you add be it mushrooms, tofu or more veggies will only contribut more flavor texture to the dish.</p>\n<figure class=\"half\">\n    <img src=\"/images/258-6.jpg\">\n    <img src=\"/images/258-7.jpg\">\n    <figcaption> Kimjang Kimchi Festival </figcaption>\n</figure> \n<p>I recently went to this annual kimjang kimchi festival event in southern Massachusetts.  Basically during the kimchi festival, families in Korea come together and make a ton of kimchi for the year.  It is an event that UNESCO has recognized as a world heritage</p>\n<figure>\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1037px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/1f59c14b0a95ae5dca2239ad2a814bce/e1ae5/258-2.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 66.63452266152362%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"258 2\" title=\"258 2\" src=\"/static/1f59c14b0a95ae5dca2239ad2a814bce/e1ae5/258-2.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/1f59c14b0a95ae5dca2239ad2a814bce/90185/258-2.jpg 450w,\n/static/1f59c14b0a95ae5dca2239ad2a814bce/7288a/258-2.jpg 900w,\n/static/1f59c14b0a95ae5dca2239ad2a814bce/e1ae5/258-2.jpg 1037w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1037px) 100vw, 1037px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n</figure> \n<figure>\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1037px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/7dfea2888e8e5a1f502658a3f0d22966/e1ae5/258-3.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 66.63452266152362%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"258 3\" title=\"258 3\" src=\"/static/7dfea2888e8e5a1f502658a3f0d22966/e1ae5/258-3.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/7dfea2888e8e5a1f502658a3f0d22966/90185/258-3.jpg 450w,\n/static/7dfea2888e8e5a1f502658a3f0d22966/7288a/258-3.jpg 900w,\n/static/7dfea2888e8e5a1f502658a3f0d22966/e1ae5/258-3.jpg 1037w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1037px) 100vw, 1037px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n</figure> \n<figure>\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1037px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/a443243281fc95ba589e1373a2406a04/e1ae5/258-4.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 66.63452266152362%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"258 4\" title=\"258 4\" src=\"/static/a443243281fc95ba589e1373a2406a04/e1ae5/258-4.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/a443243281fc95ba589e1373a2406a04/90185/258-4.jpg 450w,\n/static/a443243281fc95ba589e1373a2406a04/7288a/258-4.jpg 900w,\n/static/a443243281fc95ba589e1373a2406a04/e1ae5/258-4.jpg 1037w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1037px) 100vw, 1037px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n</figure> \n<figure>\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1037px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/97b7fa2a69653bbb492c8aaa147b3836/e1ae5/258-5.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 66.63452266152362%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"258 5\" title=\"258 5\" src=\"/static/97b7fa2a69653bbb492c8aaa147b3836/e1ae5/258-5.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/97b7fa2a69653bbb492c8aaa147b3836/90185/258-5.jpg 450w,\n/static/97b7fa2a69653bbb492c8aaa147b3836/7288a/258-5.jpg 900w,\n/static/97b7fa2a69653bbb492c8aaa147b3836/e1ae5/258-5.jpg 1037w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1037px) 100vw, 1037px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n</figure> \n<figure class=\"ingredients\" markdown=\"1\">\n<h3 id=\"vegan-kimchi-fried-rice\"><a href=\"#vegan-kimchi-fried-rice\" aria-label=\"vegan kimchi fried rice permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Vegan Kimchi Fried Rice</h3>\n<p>(Serves 2-3)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>3 tablespoons olive oil</li>\n<li>1/2 large onion</li>\n<li>1 stalk scallion</li>\n<li>1 teaspoon garlic (finely chopped)</li>\n<li>1/2 cup kimchi</li>\n<li>1/2 teaspoon soy sauce</li>\n<li>1/2 teaspoon <a href=\"http://eastmeetskitchen.com/videos/recipes/the-ultimate-vegan-fish-sauce/\">vegan fish sauce</a></li>\n<li>4 tablespoons kimchi liquid</li>\n<li>1/4 cup dried shitake mushrooms, rehydrated</li>\n<li>3 cups white rice</li>\n<li>1 teaspoon salt</li>\n<li>1 teaspoon black pepper</li>\n<li>1/4 cup tofu, cubed (optional)</li>\n</ul>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"directions\" markdown=\"1\">\n<h3 id=\"directions\"><a href=\"#directions\" aria-label=\"directions permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Directions</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Heat 2 tablespoon of the oil in a large frying pan over medium to medium high heat.  Add chopped onions with small pinch of salt and saute for 3-4 minutes until onions are translucent.  </li>\n<li>Add in garlic and cook for 30 seconds minute. </li>\n<li>Turn heat to medium high. Add in rice, kimchi, kimchi juice, soy sauce, vegan fish sauce.  Then add in the shitake mushrooms and cook for 1-2 minutes, stirring constantly.</li>\n<li>Add salt and pepper to taste.  </li>\n</ol>","timeToRead":2,"excerpt":"Fried rice is a classic dish around the world.  It's usually a mix of leftover food and in different parts of the world, those can beâ€¦","frontmatter":{"title":"Vegan Kimchi Fried Rice","image":{"feature":{"publicURL":"/static/258-5-97b7fa2a69653bbb492c8aaa147b3836.jpg","childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.5007235890014472,"src":"/static/97b7fa2a69653bbb492c8aaa147b3836/b17c1/258-5.jpg","srcSet":"/static/97b7fa2a69653bbb492c8aaa147b3836/00e5e/258-5.jpg 200w,\n/static/97b7fa2a69653bbb492c8aaa147b3836/1a903/258-5.jpg 400w,\n/static/97b7fa2a69653bbb492c8aaa147b3836/b17c1/258-5.jpg 800w,\n/static/97b7fa2a69653bbb492c8aaa147b3836/04253/258-5.jpg 1037w","sizes":"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"}}}},"feature_video":"https://www.youtube.com/embed/SJDZ8ERqpJY?rel=0","date":"2016-12-30","categories":["videos","recipes"],"tags":["videos","vegan","kimchi fried rice","fried rice","korean"]},"fields":{"slug":"/videos/recipes/vegan-kimchi-fried-rice","date":"2016-12-30T00:00:00.000Z"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/videos/recipes/vegan-kimchi-fried-rice","nextslug":"/videos/recipes/sweet-green-tea-dumplings-tang-yoon","prevslug":"/videos/recipes/vegan-peanut-butter-cups-date-sweetened"}}}